data.description: Nestled in the highly sought-after award-winning Vail School District, this stunning 2-story home boasts 4 spacious bedrooms (PLUS DEN) and 3 full bathrooms, providing ample space for family living. On the main floor, you'll find a spacious living area with easy flow into the generously-sized kitchen with plenty of counter space and storage.Moving upstairs, an expansive loft awaits, offering additional flexible space that can be transformed into a game room, home office, or whatever fits your lifestyle needs. Step outside to discover a meticulously landscaped backyard, featuring durable and attractive pavers,With its combination of style, space, and sought-after location, this home is a unique find. Don't miss your chance to secure a residence that checks all the boxes !
